{"tid":840973,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"X-men 宇宙 Dark Phoenix新預告！","createTime":"2018-09-29T08:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T10:23:35.000Z","uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cac59a01e47278bd669338ff665b200935730e7a","tid":840973,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:20:11.000Z","msg":"早在 2017 年全新《X-Men》三部曲中的第一篇章《X-Men: Dark Phoenix》（台譯：X 戰警：黑鳳凰 / 港譯：變種特攻：黑鳳凰）早已正式開拍，因為 Disney 與 21st Century Fox 的收購案才有所推遲，直到 2018 年 9 月終於迎來首波正式預告！<br />\n<br />\n「Dark Phoenix」本名 Jean Gray（ Sophie Turner 飾演），故事發生在《X-Men: Apocalypse》的十年之後，講述 X-Men 在一場外太空救援任務中，被太陽閃燄意外擊中太空梭，令 Jean Gray 無意間受到一種黑暗能量影響，逐漸化身為能力強大的 Dark Phoenix。<br />\n<br />\n《X-Men: Dark Phoenix》預告中強調了「Professor X」Charles Xavier 對於 Jean Gray 的保護措施與某極端勢力的影響，導致她成為了 Dark Phoenix，未來或將引發空前變種危機。此外多數 X-Men 們皆一同回歸，對於資深影們可謂一則大好消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0-p3YAZOtQE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0-p3YAZOtQE&d=q6AjDh8bRvErRVkXioxesbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1f51f7b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0-p3YAZOtQE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/hb1iupl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2Fhb1iupl&d=q6AjDh8bRvErRVkXioxesbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=fcbdb6b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/hb1iupl</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼apocalypse之後又一神學作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />故事都應該會係apocalypse之後既事情發展<br />\n<br />\napocalypse神學故事都已經令人津津樂道，今次既故事重心放係Jean到，一定仲正<br />\n<br />\n預期故事會多d Jean既心理，同埋Charles Erik都應該會被承先啟後左，之後會慢慢淡出。好似本身X men線係wolverine 之後去左first class，到宜家去jean同new mutant 到咁<br />\n<br />\nbtw jennifer可以抖抖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食唔到女權個浪有d可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bce21385abf7a8de47b4c5ade6a24656b2f3c37","tid":840973,"uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/162056_f17c7f9ac16e7fd884852b744c0acfac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F162056_f17c7f9ac16e7fd884852b744c0acfac.png&h=9f0fd887&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/162059_56aac8c846041e28da37f338d97ea41f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F162059_56aac8c846041e28da37f338d97ea41f.png&h=eaf07a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海報都整得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e253eb25cb5b719829000ff498639c49d2e91a6c","tid":840973,"uid":2914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"屌等左勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmo